OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772892685
OL,3,CWorkers at AWE in Berkshire to strike
OL,4,Cthis month in row over planned
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,FWorkers at the Atomic Weapons
OL,8,FEstablishment (AWE) in Berkshire will
OL,9,Fgo on strike this month in a row over
OL,10,Fplans to restructure the business.
OL,12,FThe Prospect Union says the strike
OL,13,Faction will take place on 12 March
OL,14,Fwith a further strike scheduled for 26
OL,15,FMarch.
OL,17,FAction short of a strike is already
OL,18,Funderway and will run continuously.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
