PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772892685
OL,3,CWorkers at AWE in Berkshire to strike
OL,4,Cthis month in row over planned
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,FThe union says the ballot results,
OL,8,Fwhich cover staff working at AWE sites
OL,9,Fincluding at Aldermaston and
OL,10,FBurghfield, were 81% in favour of
OL,11,Fstrike action over what it describes
OL,12,Fas "a litany of errors and failure to
OL,13,Fconsult from senior management".
OL,15,FThe union says AWE told staff in
OL,16,FNovember it would embark on a
OL,17,Frestructuring programme which could
OL,18,Fpotentially create 800 redundancies. A
OL,19,Ffurther 750 posts are being recruited
OL,20,Ffor.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772892685
OL,3,CWorkers at AWE in Berkshire to strike
OL,4,Cthis month in row over planned
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,FMike Clancy, General Secretary of
OL,8,FProspect, said: "Our members are the
OL,9,Fcountry's leading experts in their
OL,10,Ffield and take huge pride in the job
OL,11,Fthey do on behalf of the nation.
OL,13,F"They deserve a full and honest
OL,14,Faccount of the justification for these
OL,15,Fchanges, and the consequences for the
OL,16,Ffuture of the organisation, with a
OL,17,Fchance to have their own voices
OL,18,Fmeaningfully heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772892685
OL,3,CWorkers at AWE in Berkshire to strike
OL,4,Cthis month in row over planned
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,F"The chaotic and partial provision of
OL,8,Finformation during this process has
OL,9,Fseriously damaged the relationship
OL,10,Fbetween AWE staff and their leadership
OL,11,Fand is the root cause of this action.
OL,13,F"We have been clear with management
OL,14,Fthroughout this process about the
OL,15,Fsteps they need to take but, while
OL,16,Fsome progress has been made, the core
OL,17,Fissues remain unresolved, leaving us
OL,18,Fno choice but to push ahead with this
OL,19,Faction."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772892685
OL,3,CWorkers at AWE in Berkshire to strike
OL,4,Cthis month in row over planned
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,FA Ministry of Defence spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are aware of Prospect's
OL,9,Fplanned strike action and continue to
OL,10,Furge dialogue, meaningful consultation
OL,11,Fand a constructive resolution between
OL,12,FAWE and Prospect on the issues raised.
OL,14,F"Pre-planned contingency measures will
OL,15,Fbe implemented to maintain defence
OL,16,Foutputs and the safety and security of
OL,17,FAWE's sites.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
