OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772892685
OL,3,CWorkers at AWE in Berkshire to strike
OL,4,Cthis month in row over planned
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,F"The AWE workforce is being reshaped
OL,8,Fto deliver on the government's
OL,9,Fcommitment to the nuclear deterrent,
OL,10,Frefocussing resources to build
OL,11,Fcapability, and AWE will continue to
OL,12,Foperate with approximately 9,500
OL,13,Femployees."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
